---
title: Indian Haloumi & Veggie Biryani with Roasted Cashews & Currants
description: Forget what you think you know about biryani - this veggie version, using haloumi instead of lamb, just goes to show that rules are made to be broken! It's sweet, spicy, satisfying and just the thing to make you smile.
